3402625\" width=600 height=54 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/807880/extras/926a9af46543b34e8e8dc89cb70ab670.webm?t=1613402625\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/807880/extras/926a9af46543b34e8e8dc89cb70ab670.mp4?t=1613402625\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Bomb to blow up several sectors at once.<br></li><li>Grid to delete all creatures of one species from the field.<br></li><li>Magic Hammer to eliminate one dweller from the field.<br></li><li>Lightning to eliminate any horizontal row.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >IN THE SEARCH OF ANCIENT GOLD</h2>Seek and you shall find. Complete all the levels and find the ancient treasure!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >USE BONUSES WISELY</h2>Know when to use each bonus to reach the best effect <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/807880/extras/cd4823ef8983df8b6a01d95916f4a70f.poster.avif?t=1613402625\" width=600 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/807880/extras/cd4823ef8983df8b6a01d95916f4a70f.webm?t=1613402625\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/807880/extras/cd4823ef8983df8b6a01d95916f4a70f.mp4?t=1613402625\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
